STATE of North Carolina
v.
Stanley Lorenzo WILLIAMS. No. 507P05-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 29, 2006. Stanley L. Williams, Pro Se. Christopher W. Brooks, Assistant Attorney General, Roxann Vaneekhoven, District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition for Writ of Prohibition filed by Defendant on the 9th day of May 2006 in this matter, the following order was entered and is:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 29th day of June 2006."
